WEBVTT

00:03.530 --> 00:05.539
Here's a fun Postal fact.

00:05.563 --> 00:07.773
Yeah, the inner side
of our mailbox

00:07.797 --> 00:09.545
is under federal jurisdiction.

00:09.568 --> 00:11.615
So, if you broke
my right thumb,

00:11.639 --> 00:13.396
that's Pasadena city police.

00:13.420 --> 00:15.281
But if you broke
my left thumb,

00:15.305 --> 00:16.863
that's the FBI.

00:18.432 --> 00:20.893
If I'm going to jail, I'm killing him,
not breaking his thumb.

00:20.917 --> 00:22.201
No.

00:22.492 --> 00:24.968
Oh, I got a letter
from my Meemaw.

00:25.390 --> 00:26.669
Umm. Smell this.

00:27.741 --> 00:28.459
What is that?

00:28.551 --> 00:31.189
Uh, roses, bengay,
and Dr. Schools' foot powder.

00:32.137 --> 00:34.409
Yeah, "Grandma",
by Calvin Klein.

00:36.525 --> 00:38.456
Yeah, the last time I got
a hand written letter,

00:38.480 --> 00:41.653
it was from someone who told me
I parked like a blind person.

00:41.677 --> 00:43.224
That someone has a name.

00:43.248 --> 00:44.921
Uh, thank you.

00:46.781 --> 00:48.831
Oh, Meemaw got
a new set of teeth.

00:50.081 --> 00:51.825
Oh, but then
she found her old ones.

00:53.095 --> 00:55.441
Oh, so now the new ones are
just gonna be her church teeth.

00:57.487 --> 00:59.413
Fun. Like your
Comic-Con Spock ears

00:59.437 --> 01:01.336
and your around
the house Spock ears.

01:03.702 --> 01:05.591
***

01:08.482 --> 01:10.282
Oh, my goodness,
she's coming to visit!

01:10.284 --> 01:12.718
Oh, it'll be nice
to finally meet her.

01:12.720 --> 01:14.486
Oh, you are going
to love her.

01:14.488 --> 01:17.289
She is the kindest, sweetest
woman you'll ever meet.

01:17.291 --> 01:20.192
Yeah, unless you're a gopher
digging up her vegetable garden.

01:21.362 --> 01:22.595
In that case, you can expect

01:22.597 --> 01:25.931
to have your head bashed in
with a shovel.

01:25.933 --> 01:29.568
♪ Our whole universe
was in a hot, dense state ♪

01:29.570 --> 01:32.905
♪ Then nearly 14 billion years
ago expansion started... Wait! ♪

01:32.907 --> 01:34.540
♪ The Earth began to cool ♪

01:34.542 --> 01:37.076
♪ The autotrophs began to drool,
Neanderthals developed tools ♪

01:37.078 --> 01:39.745
♪ We built the Wall ♪
♪<i> We built the pyramids</i> ♪

01:39.747 --> 01:42.414
♪ Math, Science, History,
unraveling the mystery ♪

01:42.416 --> 01:44.316
♪ That all started
with a big bang ♪

01:44.318 --> 01:46.266
